commit.message:
[travis] Cleanup

- xenial is default dist in travis
- no need to specify basepython
- reorder travis steps to match tox envs

Add migration for test models.

In Django 2.2, tests fail without it because constraints are checked
after tables for apps without migrations are created but before tables
for apps with migrations are created. The test models have foreign keys
to django.contrib.sites which has migrations.
Add Jazzband upload endpoint to travis config.
